OL,5, The family of an 11-year-old boy who   
OL,6, died after being hit by a bin lorry in 
OL,7, Edinburgh have described him as "the   
OL,8, perfect son".                          
OL,10,FThomas Wong was riding his bike when he
OL,11,Fwas involved in a collision with the   
OL,12,Fvehicle on Whitehouse Road, at about   
OL,13,F08:20 on Friday.                       
OL,15,FPolice Scotland said he was pronounced 
OL,16,Fdead at the scene.                     
OL,18,FIn a statement, released by the force  
OL,19,Fon Sunday, Thomas' family said they    
OL,20,Fwere "utterly heartbroken".            
